title: 5 industries that are getting disrupted by Computer Vision on Cloud and on Edge
description: Manufacturing, Media, Finance - these are just a few of the industries being disrupted by the application of state-of-the-art Computer Vision. Join Corporate Vice President Lila Tretikov, as she shows how key technical advances are generating business value for customers with Azure AI, Robotic Process Automation, and Mixed Reality.
